<div id="About"></div>

<div class="container py-5 align-content-center mt-5">
    <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="about-section text-center">
                <h1 class="fw-bold">About Our Voting System</h1>
                <p class="mt-3">
                    Our online voting system aims to modernize the electoral process by replacing the traditional ballot system. Leveraging technology, this system enhances efficiency, reduces costs, and ensures transparency.
                    It eliminates geographical barriers, simplifies vote casting, and accelerates result generation. Our solution is secure, scalable, and designed to meet the needs of contemporary elections.
                </p>
                <div class="row mt-5">
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                        <div class="card mb-3 mb-md-5 shadow">
                            <div class="card-body bg-black">
                                <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">Secure Voting</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">Advanced encryption ensures your vote remains confidential and tamper-proof.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                        <div class="card shadow mb-3 mb-md-5">
                            <div class="card-body bg-black">
                                <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">Faster Results</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">Automated tallying provides instant results, eliminating delays.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                        <div class="card shadow mb-3 mb-md-5">
                            <div class="card-body bg-black">
                                <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">Cost Effective</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">Save resources by replacing costly paper-based systems.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="StepsToVote"></div>

<div class="container py-5 align-content-center" id="StepsToVote">
    <div class="text-center m-5">
        <h1 class="fw-bold">How to Vote</h1>
        <p class="mt-3">Follow these simple steps to cast your vote online securely and efficiently.</p>
    </div>
